@startuml
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

rectangle "User\n(Finder / Loser)" as User <<External Entity>>
usecase "4.0\nManage\nOwnership Claims" as P4
database "D3: Claims DB\n(MongoDB)" as D3
database "D2: Items DB\n(MongoDB)" as D2

User --> P4 : Claim Request, Security Answer,\nApproval/Rejection
P4 --> D3 : Save/Update Claim Record
D3 --> P4 : Claim Status Data
P4 --> D2 : Update Item Status\n(Open -> Closed)
D2 --> P4 : Item Ownership Data\n(For Verification)
P4 --> User : Contact Info (If Approved),\nStatus Update
@enduml
